original: Falck, Knut Ulrich Moritz Rudolf, jägmästare, Växjö, f. 27/10/80 i Malmö av fältläk. Johan August F. o. Char-ilfoitte Åberg. G. 11 m. Inignid Hiul’t-gren. — Studiex. 99, utex. fr. skogs-inst. 04. E. jägmäst. 05, skogstaxer. i Smål. distr. 14, jägmäst. i Sunnerho revir 19, i Värends revir 28-43, pens. Skr.: art. i fackpressen. RVO 33.
translated: Falck, Knut Ulrich Moritz Rudolf, forester, Växjö, b. 27/10/80 in Malmö to field doctor Johan August F. and Char-ilfoitte Åberg. Married 11/xx to Inignid Hiul’t-gren. — Graduated 99, graduated from Forestry Institute 04. Became a forester in 1905, forest appraiser in Småland district in 1914, forester in Sunnerho district in 1919, in Värends district from 1928-1943, retired. Wrote articles for professional journals. Awarded the Order of Vasa in 1933.
